00:38:13.520 --> 00:38:16.160
with this crusade
she's on, please

00:38:16.160 --> 00:38:17.230
look at hashtag #TeamEva.

00:38:19.790 --> 00:38:22.220
EVA KOR: I want to jump
in also with something,

00:38:22.220 --> 00:38:25.640
because I have an app.

